<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Supplement</hi> to SPW’s <hi rend="italic">Manual of the Mollusca</hi> [1851–6]. Praises SPW’s work. "What an amount of labour is condensed in your little volume! … I fully believe &amp; hope that you will reap the only reward worth having, the consciousness that you have done good service to the cause of Science."</p> 
